newsitem.title: MEXICO: Mexico's TIIE 28-day rate falls to 32.3150 pct.
newsitem.headline: Mexico's TIIE 28-day rate falls to 32.3150 pct.

text.p: Mexico's 28-day interbank interest rate fell by 18.50 basis points to 32.3150 percent on Tuesday, from 32.5000 percent on Monday, Banco de Mexico said.
The TIIE is a market-weighted average interbank rate that is revised daily.
